---
title: Loaded Mexican Bacon & Corn Fritter Bowl with Garlic Rice, Tomato Salsa & Smokey Aioli
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet, and are set off perfectly by an A-team of tangy smokey aioli, Cheddar
cheese and zesty salsa. If you fancy it, you could also break out your favourite hot sauce for these bad boys!
